Rotate Array by One

Link : https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/cyclically-rotate-an-array-by-one2614/1

Implementation:

class Solution {
    public void rotate(int[] arr) {
        // code here
        int n= arr.length;
        int last = arr[n-1];
        for(int i = n-1; i > 0; i--) {
             arr[i] = arr[i-1];
            }
        arr[0] = last;
    }
}

Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)
